0.1.0

* parse dates from a given format
* generates ActiveRecord errors for invalid dates
* provides formatted dates

0.1.1

* support to suffix customization

0.2.0

* date format is defined at locale file
* dropped :format option from method flexible_date
* added i18n support for error messages
* removed deprecated Gem::Specification#has_rdoc= from gem specification

0.3.0

* allow blank fields
* support to :if option

